		<descriptionSet>
			<description source=" " lang="en" script="latn">On this advertisement for Scandale underwear, a woman is jumping high up in the air next to her black silhouette wearing the advertised product. An elaborate advertising text is printed on the right side of the image.</description>
		</descriptionSet>
		<inscriptionSet>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">So light! So comfortable and
Supple -</text>
			</inscription>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">assuring every Woman and Girl of the
greatest ease and perfect control. To
wear a SCANDALE, all elastic net belt or
corselet means easy living, happy care-
free days. Any discomfort or difficulty
which you may ever have had with your
foundations will be done away with for
good when you S C A N D A L E - ISE.
Neither repeated washings nor the most
tropical conditions, can in any
way affect SCANDALE foundations. You
can even wear a SCANDALE model
without suspenders and yet it will never
ride up - it fits snugly and comfortably and with just
that right amount of "give".</text>
			</inscription>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">Hints on buying your foundation:
1. Always be fitted if you can, and in no case choose an under-
size.
2. Remember that a good foundation is important for your
general well-being. 
3. It is to your advantage to buy two similar models and wear
each on alternative weeks, they will last longer.
4. Remember that there are over 40 different SCANDALE
models, made in 5 strengths, so as to suit every type of figure.</text>
			</inscription>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">SCANDALE
There are no substitutes.</text>
			</inscription>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">At all leading stores and corsetieres throughout the World. Write for Free
Illustrated Brochure No. I. B. 30, and if any difficulty in obtaining, for name of
nearest stockist to: Petit &amp; Co., Ltd., (Wholesale only) 81, Great Portland
Street, London, W. 1.</text>
			</inscription>
